snippet.textDisplay:
Some people complaining about more punjabi songs. One of the reasons is that most punjabi songs are from Sufi's Poetry like Baba Bulley Shah' kalam. Secondly urdu and punjabi has the largest audience in Indo Pak , so more songs makes sense. 
But i also agree that there should be more local songs. Post Rohail is more commercial era of coke studio, less experiments, less fusion. Rohail's time was international fusion and here we are complaining about less exposure of our local languages.
